how to play rock paper scissors

rock > Scissors
paper > Rock
scissors > Paper

inputs
  -random generated selection of rock, paper, or scissors from computer
  -input selection or rock, paper, or scissors from user
  -restart function to start game over again
  -
  
outputs
  -message/text:
    *"You win! Rock beats scissors"
    *"You win! Paper beats rock"
    *"You win! Scissors beats paper"
    *"You lose, rock beats scissors"
    *"You lose, paper beats rock"
    *"You lose, scissors beats paper"
    *"Congrats, You won!"
    *"Game over, better luck next time"
  -
    
computer picks a random selection of either rock, paper, or scissors
player imputs a selection of either rock, paper, or scissors
if player imput is < computer generated input, display "you lose" message
if player imput is > computer generated imput, display "you win" message
repeat for 5 rounds and decalre a winner at the end of 5th game
reset number of tries and history of tries to start game over again from the beginning

